<div class="comment-item" id=5287812 data-cid="5287812" data-target_id="5655635" data-target_kind="1012">
    <div class="pic">
    </div>
    <div class="content report-comment">
        <div class="author">
          2013-01-06 17:43:20 
          <a href="http://www.douban.com/people/27842842/">Jay</a> 
        </div>


        
        <p>　　楼主的评价和电影一样又臭又长，噶难看的一部007居然说不辱系列，导演倒的昏昏欲睡，弄个SKYFALL的旧宅就刺激到楼主的G点了嘛。</p>

        <div class="op-lnks">
